│ DL.getPointerSizeInBits(GEPLHS->getPointerAddressSpace())](GEPNoWrapFlags NW) {\n │
│ if (ICmpInst::isEquality(Cond))\n      // Equality folding is only sound if       │
│ pointer arithmetic cannot wrap\n      // between distinct indices. Allow fold     │
│ when we have explicit no-wrap\n      // flags (nuw or nusw) or when the pointer   │
│ type is sufficiently wide\n      // (avoid the known miscompile on extremely      │
│ narrow pointer types such as\n      // 8-bit). This preserves existing folds for  │
│ normal targets while\n      // preventing the unsound transformation for tiny     │
